<collectingCountry box="[678,774,942,967]" name="Ecuador" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Ecuador</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="36.[151,1437,402,1147]" box="[199,387,978,1003]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,262,978,1003]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Host.</emphasis>
Unknown.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[199,1425,1014,1039]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="36.[151,1437,402,1147]" box="[199,1425,1014,1039]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1014,1039]" pageId="36" pageNumber="37">Etymology.</emphasis>
A noun from Latin for &quot;black line&quot; referring to the distinct black line on the oviscape membrane.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
